      "review_summary": "The PR changes media CLI audio output resolution and tests so recognized Whisper, parakeet, and local-whisper transcript files are authoritative instead of falling back to stdout when inferred `.txt` output is empty or missing.\n\nPR surface: Source +30, Tests +287. Total +317 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main falls through from empty or missing inferred transcript files to stdout, and the PR proof shows the fixed local-whisper path with a real Telegram audio message. I did not run a live repro because this review is read-only.",
